People saying, oh I'm launching my game next week.

125
00:08:19,964 --> 00:08:22,426
Because in 2018, everybody's inbox is full.

126
00:08:22,426 --> 00:08:26,389
So you need to give them as much time as possible.

127
00:08:26,389 --> 00:08:29,731
