00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:43,161
before I actually launch it.

132
00:08:43,784 --> 00:08:47,688
which is a month and a half early.

133
00:08:47,688 --> 00:08:51,052
So when you put that in the grand scheme of things,

134
00:08:51,052 --> 00:08:52,914
it becomes a big difference, a big change.

