00:26:38,843 --> 00:26:40,344
It's super cheap.

411
00:26:41,294 --> 00:26:47,717
But you then have two or three competitions a week, no problem, less than $20 a month.

412
00:26:47,717 --> 00:26:49,378
Bargain.

413
00:26:49,378 --> 00:26:54,600
And it's a good way to just get people interacting, and you do it so.

414
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:59,662
So the way that we do it is, we have a level up system in our Discord.

415
00:26:59,662 --> 00:27:06,405
So the more that you chat, the more that you post, the more that you interact, the higher your level goes.

416
00:27:06,405 --> 00:27:10,587
And the higher your level is, the more likely you are to win prizes.

417
00:27:11,317 --> 00:27:14,697
So people talk and interact because there's extra motivation.

418
00:27:14,697 --> 00:27:17,218
So do things like that.

419
00:27:17,218 --> 00:27:26,720
So what I'm going to do now is I'm going to kind of give you an overview of a game launch.

