00:30:20,915 --> 00:30:27,079
Woo! The game will be coming out July 1st. Send that press release to the press.

466
00:30:27,079 --> 00:30:31,202
At the same time, send your embargoed press release.

467
00:30:31,202 --> 00:30:34,124
So you basically send two press kits at one time.

468
00:30:34,124 --> 00:30:38,487
One with the saying, saying, hey the game's coming out on July 1st.

469
00:30:38,487 --> 00:30:49,075
Another one with a key to the game, with all the information about the launch, and with the embargo information as well.

470
00:30:49,075 --> 00:30:49,235
In June...

471
00:30:49,582 --> 00:30:56,284
you're still preparing all of your social media, you're preparing the launch date stuff,

472
00:30:56,284 --> 00:31:02,985
and you're updating all of the bugs that you will still be finding, because you will still

473
00:31:02,985 --> 00:31:07,687
be finding bugs at this point. And you pray. You pray that everything will go well, and

474
00:31:07,687 --> 00:31:14,788
then in July, boom, your game's out. So that's what six months looks like. It goes very,

